ithonline\/2019\/08\/09\/allah-boasts-pilgrims-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26044,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Allah boasts of the pilgrims at Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty boasts to His angels of the pilgrims on the afternoon of the day of Arafat, saying: Look at My servants, coming to Me disheveled and dusty!\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 7089 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15670,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/fasting-or-not-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26044,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Fasting or not on the day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I have performed the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he did not fast during Arafat. I performed it with Abu Bakr and he did not fast, with Umar and he did not fast, and with Uthman and he did not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23690,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/06\/hajj-itself-is-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26044,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Arafat: Hajj culminates in day of &#8216;Arafah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 6, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdu Rahman ibn Ya\u2019mar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hajj is Arafat. Whoever reaches the night of Arafat before the rising of the sun at dawn the next day, he has completed his pilgrimage.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3016 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8781,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/24\/fasting-arafah-ashura\/","url_meta":{"origin":26044,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: Sins erased by fasting &#8216;Arafat, &#8216;Ashura","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked about fasting the day of 'Arafat, and he said, \u201cIt will\u00a0expiate the sins of the previous and upcoming years.\u201d Then, the Prophet was asked about fasting the day of 'Ashura, and he said, \u201cIt will expiate the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/23\/best-dua-yawm-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26044,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Arafah: Best supplication on day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 23, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best supplication is that which is made on the day of Arafat. The best of it is what was said by myself and the Prophets before me, 'There is no God but Allah alone, without any\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26044","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26044"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26044\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26044"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=26044"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=26044"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}